490
00:53:00,320 --> 00:53:02,440
Guard 'em, Prince. Guard 'em.

491
00:53:06,000 --> 00:53:07,960
Noisy bastards.

492
00:53:09,440 --> 00:53:12,280
If I have to come down there,
you're gonna be sorry.

493
00:53:15,560 --> 00:53:19,080
Roach, you're shot.
