506
00:55:42,400 --> 00:55:45,280
Oh, I got him good.
And the black one, too.

507
00:55:50,840 --> 00:55:52,440
Shut the fuck up!

508
00:55:56,720 --> 00:55:58,800
What the hell's wrong with him?

509
00:56:02,680 --> 00:56:04,760
- He said he killed you.
- He exaggerated.

510
00:56:12,040 --> 00:56:13,720
Come on!

511
00:56:14,400 --> 00:56:15,960
Stay!

512
00:56:25,680 --> 00:56:27,920
Move. If he finds us,
he'll shoot through the walls.

513
00:56:28,080 --> 00:56:30,720
- My dress is stuck on something.
- Oh, great

514
00:56:35,040 --> 00:56:38,360
Uh-oh. You gotta keep goin', Alice.
Come on.

515
00:56:43,040 --> 00:56:46,720
Burn in hell for gettin' free,
and burn in hell for showin' the way!

516
00:57:00,800 --> 00:57:01,880
