517
00:57:07,600 --> 00:57:09,960
Burn! Burn!

518
00:57:10,480 --> 00:57:12,400
Burn in hell!

519
00:57:15,280 --> 00:57:17,040
Burn!

520
00:57:25,640 --> 00:57:28,800
Alice, he's comin' closer.
We gotta get outta here.

521
00:57:58,640 --> 00:58:01,000
- Which way?
- Only Roach knew the way.

522
00:58:01,680 --> 00:58:03,320
So we'll explore.

523
00:58:03,600 --> 00:58:05,520
Gonna find you!

524
00:58:05,920 --> 00:58:08,000
- I gotta sneeze.
- Gonna kill ya!

525
