526
00:58:33,360 --> 00:58:36,240
- We gotta be careful.
- Real careful.

527
00:58:37,120 --> 00:58:40,120
- Do you think you got him?
- We'll soon find out. Come on.

528
00:58:40,560 --> 00:58:42,680
Come on. Kill. Kill. Kill.

529
00:58:42,960 --> 00:58:45,440
Kill! Kill 'em, Prince. Kill 'em!

530
00:58:45,840 --> 00:58:47,080
Kill 'em!

531
00:58:48,040 --> 00:58:50,560
