541
01:00:26,680 --> 01:00:28,800
I got him! I got him!

542
01:00:29,080 --> 01:00:31,600
I got him, I got him, I got him!
I got him, I got him!

543
01:00:32,440 --> 01:00:35,000
I got him, I got him, I got him!
I got him, I got him!

544
01:00:35,320 --> 01:00:37,640
I got him, I got him, I got him!

