547
01:00:46,320 --> 01:00:48,800
There's light up there. Come on.

548
01:01:00,120 --> 01:01:02,480
I know you're in there,
you little piece of shit.

549
01:01:03,320 --> 01:01:04,960
- Oh, no!

550
01:01:10,760 --> 01:01:12,240
Oh, shit.

551
01:01:12,280 --> 01:01:14,240
You killed Prince!

552
01:01:35,920 --> 01:01:38,280
Look. You can see
the lights of the ghetto from here.

553
01:01:38,920 --> 01:01:41,520
I never thought
smog could smell so good.

554
01:01:42,800 --> 01:01:44,920
- Help!
- Sh!

555
01:01:45,520 --> 01:01:48,360
- We might have to climb down.
- There's nothing to hold on to.

556
01:01:48,440 --> 01:01:50,320
It's just a straight drop off the roof.

557
01:01:51,000 --> 01:01:52,520
- Wait a minute.
- What?

558
01:01:52,600 --> 01:01:55,960
The water in the garden.
I think it's right under this window.

559
01:01:56,720 --> 01:01:59,120
If we take a jump off the edge,
we might be able to hit it.

560
01:01:59,480 --> 01:02:01,880
- I don't know how deep it is.
- I hear 'em!

561
01:02:02,400 --> 01:02:05,360
- Alice, come on. We gotta jump!
- I can't! I'm afraid.

562
01:02:06,320 --> 01:02:07,720
You upstairs, Alice?

563
01:02:07,960 --> 01:02:09,560
- Alice!
- What's out there?

564
01:02:12,000 --> 01:02:13,480
There he is!

565
01:02:19,160 --> 01:02:21,080
What were you doin' with him? Come here.

566
01:02:21,480 --> 01:02:23,240
Alice! Alice!

567
01:02:29,400 --> 01:02:31,920
No! No! No! No!

568
01:02:39,560 --> 01:02:40,400
Damn it.

569
01:02:55,560 --> 01:02:57,320
I'll be back, Alice! Hang on!

570
01:02:59,560 --> 01:03:01,280
Bastard!

571
01:03:02,760 --> 01:03:04,800
Never shoot your gun outside!

572
01:03:07,120 --> 01:03:09,560
- He got away.
- Come back inside.

573
01:03:14,560 --> 01:03:16,280
Damn it.

574
01:03:18,200 --> 01:03:20,160
Bad boy! Go on.

575
01:03:24,440 --> 01:03:26,160
Go to your room and get into your suit.

576
01:03:29,040 --> 01:03:32,920
If these had come from anybody else,
I'd make you take 'em straight back.

577
01:03:33,680 --> 01:03:35,760
- You know that?
- Yes, sir.

578
01:03:37,560 --> 01:03:40,520
Well, figurin' the rarity of these,...

579
01:03:40,920 --> 01:03:44,040
