to pay your rent for a while.

580
01:03:44,680 --> 01:03:46,800
Say, to the year 2OOO.

581
01:03:48,520 --> 01:03:52,040
- And Mama's operation?
- And your mama's operation.

582
01:03:54,600 --> 01:03:57,000
Keep hold of these till tomorrow.

583
01:03:57,440 --> 01:03:59,800
I'm gonna order
an ambulance for your mama.

584
01:04:00,320 --> 01:04:04,680
Tomorrow we'll take those to
a good coin dealer, and we'll dll be smilin'.

585
01:04:05,360 --> 01:04:07,400
Meanwhile, you be careful.

586
01:04:07,800 --> 01:04:11,200
That brother-sister act you messed with
are evil, plain and simple.

587
01:04:11,920 --> 01:04:14,120
Wait a minute. Brother and sister?

588
01:04:14,400 --> 01:04:18,920
Brother and sister. Tail end of
the craziest family you ever heard of.

589
01:04:19,840 --> 01:04:22,520
Every generation more insane
than the one before.

590
01:04:22,840 --> 01:04:25,760
Started out as a family
runnin' a funeral home,...

591
01:04:26,000 --> 01:04:29,760
..sellin' cheap coffins for expensive prices.

592
01:04:30,640 --> 01:04:33,120
Then they got their fingers
into real estate,...

593
01:04:33,720 --> 01:04:36,360
..started makin' a lot of money
takin' over people's homes.

594
01:04:36,480 --> 01:04:38,880
The more money they got,
the greedier they got.

595
01:04:39,520 --> 01:04:42,160
The greedier they got,
the crazier they got.

596
01:04:42,360 --> 01:04:45,440
All sorts of rumors about
what's gone on in that place.

597
01:04:47,040 --> 01:04:50,240
Never proved it because
the police didn't take it serious.

598
01:04:50,680 --> 01:04:54,720
But believe me, when I was a kid,
none of us ever walked past that house.

599
01:05:02,760 --> 01:05:04,840
You OK, Fool?

600
01:05:05,080 --> 01:05:08,720
I was just tellin' Mama that
I did somethin' wrong. Real wrong.

601
01:05:09,680 --> 01:05:11,800
And now I gotta do somethin' right.

602
01:05:11,960 --> 01:05:14,160
I done the tarot cards on you again.

603
01:05:14,640 --> 01:05:18,280
They come up real scary. Don't go
messin' with them people again.

604
01:05:22,600 --> 01:05:25,680
Somebody has to.
And maybe that means me.

605
01:05:27,080 --> 01:05:30,360
Anyway, I made a promise to Alice.
And I'm gonna keep it.

606
01:06:00,680 --> 01:06:02,640
- 14th Precinct.
- Hello. Police?

607
01:06:03,240 --> 01:06:04,120
Yes.

608
01:06:04,400 --> 01:06:06,280
I'd like to report a case of child abuse.

609
01:06:06,360 --> 01:06:08,960
- All right. When did this happen?
- Right now.

610
01:06:13,000 --> 01:06:15,760
- Is this real or what?
- Bogus. The place is clean.

611
01:06:16,360 --> 01:06:19,760
The people don't even have kids.
They have coffee, though.

612
01:06:20,640 --> 01:06:23,240
I'm gonna go upstairs
and look around.

613
01:06:24,920 --> 01:06:27,720
- More coffee?
- No, thank you. I've had plenty.

614
01:06:35,960 --> 01:06:40,160
I'm so sorry you all had to come out
at such an hour for such a silly thing.

615
01:06:46,040 --> 01:06:49,040
But, you know, it's better
there are a few false calls...

616
01:06:49,400 --> 01:06:52,480
..if we can prevent
just one child from being abused.

617
01:06:53,240 --> 01:06:56,040
- Mm-hm. Absolutely right.
- Cream and sugar?

618
01:07:23,440 --> 01:07:26,920
Nice furniture. You didn't get that stuff
at Price Club, that's for sure.

619
01:07:27,760 --> 01:07:29,880
- It's been in the family for years.
- Yeah?

620
01:07:30,160 --> 01:07:34,000
Used to be the house
was used for, uh... business.

621
01:07:34,480 --> 01:07:36,160
- No kidding?
- Sergeant?

622
01:07:36,880 --> 01:07:38,680
There's something you might wanna see.

623
01:07:38,800 --> 01:07:40,800
- What?
- Take a look.

624
01:07:50,320 --> 01:07:54,360
- I thought you said you had no kids.
- Alice left us a long time ago.

625
01:07:54,920 --> 01:07:57,280
The Lord saw fit to come and take her.

626
01:07:57,800 --> 01:07:59,920
Never touched the room since.

627
01:08:00,280 --> 01:08:04,920
We're foolish, I suppose, but...
in a sense, she still lives here.

628
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:12,080
- And always will.
- My apologies.

629
01:08:12,400 --> 01:08:14,160
It must be very painful for you.

630
01:08:14,320 --> 01:08:17,240
I'm sorry about this.
This should have never happened.

631
01:08:17,680 --> 01:08:19,960
No need to apologize.
We wanna be helpful.

632
01:08:21,520 --> 01:08:24,400
- Good night, sir.
- Thanks for the refreshments.

633
01:08:24,880 --> 01:08:26,200
You're welcome.

634
01:08:26,320 --> 01:08:30,440
I don't wanna see
another cop or cookie in my life!

635
01:08:32,160 --> 01:08:34,440
I don't know which one makes me sicker.

636
01:08:34,920 --> 01:08:36,920
May they burn in hell.

637
01:08:38,280 --> 01:08:40,880
Forever and ever in hell.

638
01:08:56,400 --> 01:08:58,280
- The shelf worked.
- Yup.

639
01:08:59,680 --> 01:09:02,360
Always does. Simple works best.

640
01:09:04,880 --> 01:09:06,640
Gotta get a new dog tomorrow.

641
01:09:06,840 --> 01:09:08,720
A good big one.

642
01:09:16,320 --> 01:09:19,680
I was worried. The police left
the back door open for so long.

643
01:09:20,000 --> 01:09:22,080
- So?
- I couldn't watch it all the time.

644
01:09:22,320 --> 01:09:25,640
- Think any of 'em got out?
- Nah. They were pretty out of it.

645
01:09:26,400 --> 01:09:28,680
- What'd you use?
- Horse tranquilizers.

646
01:10:33,960 --> 01:10:36,480
Tomorrow I'm gonna look
for the Bear Trooper.

647
01:10:36,800 --> 01:10:38,960
- Where would you look?
- The ghetto.

648
01:10:39,360 --> 01:10:41,680
I'll find him. And I'll kill him.

649
01:10:45,760 --> 01:10:47,680
- Night, Mama.
- Night, Daddy.

650
01:10:48,640 --> 01:10:51,760
- Say your prayers like a good boy.
- Oh! I forgot.

651
01:10:53,320 --> 01:10:55,600
Now I lay me down to sleep,...

652
01:10:56,400 --> 01:10:58,880
Now I lay me down to sleep,...

653
01:10:59,760 --> 01:11:02,960
.. I pray the Lord my soul to keep.

654
01:11:03,400 --> 01:11:07,200
If I should kill before I wake,...

655
01:11:07,640 --> 01:11:10,840
.. I pray the Lord my soul to take.

656
01:11:11,280 --> 01:11:13,760
.. I pray the Lord my soul to take.

657
01:11:25,520 --> 01:11:28,000
Ah! You miserable little shit!

658
01:11:31,480 --> 01:11:32,840
Shut up!

659
01:11:37,360 --> 01:11:39,360
You hurt my baby!

660
01:11:42,000 --> 01:11:44,000
Get him! Get him!

661
01:11:55,520 --> 01:11:57,600
- Get him! Get him!

662
01:11:59,640 --> 01:12:01,240
"Downstairs door. "

663
01:12:22,440 --> 01:12:24,840
- Did you get him?
- He's fast, damn it!

664
01:12:25,320 --> 01:12:26,920
Open the kitchen.

665
01:12:32,640 --> 01:12:34,760
Oh, shit!

666
01:12:35,200 --> 01:12:37,520
What happened? Did he get out?

667
01:12:38,920 --> 01:12:40,720
Oh! Burn in hell.

668
01:12:41,720 --> 01:12:43,480
Burn in hell.

669
01:12:43,640 --> 01:12:46,840
What about Alice?
What'll we do with her?

670
01:12:47,480 --> 01:12:49,640
Let her hang up there all night.

671
01:12:50,360 --> 01:12:54,560
- She's terrified of the attic.
- I know. It serves her right.

672
01:13:20,520 --> 01:13:22,440
- Alice!
- Fool?

673
01:13:23,600 --> 01:13:25,560
Are you OK?

674
01:13:26,960 --> 01:13:29,040
Can you get any more of these bricks out?

675
01:13:29,400 --> 01:13:31,600
- I can't. They've got me stuck.
- How?

676
01:13:32,640 --> 01:13:34,920
I'm tied to a bolt in the chimney.

677
01:13:37,040 --> 01:13:37,880
This one?

678
01:13:44,960 --> 01:13:46,920
Yes.

679
01:13:47,040 --> 01:13:48,520
- Hi.
- Hi.

680
01:13:51,880 --> 01:13:55,040
Let's see if we can get
some more of these bricks out.

681
01:13:57,920 --> 01:13:59,880
Sh! Get down!

682
01:14:14,920 --> 01:14:16,960
Let me down, please.

683
01:14:22,480 --> 01:14:26,040
Daddy! Come down from there
and help me to bed!

684
01:14:27,120 --> 01:14:28,840
Daddy!

685
01:14:37,920 --> 01:14:39,880
I said now!

686
01:14:42,960 --> 01:14:44,960
He's gone. Fool?

687
01:14:46,280 --> 01:14:48,040
Fool?

688
01:14:50,400 --> 01:14:52,160
Meet me at the window.
You know the one.

689
01:14:52,240 --> 01:14:53,400
OK.

690
01:14:54,240 --> 01:14:56,640
- You find him, bring him back to me.
- I will!

691
01:14:57,080 --> 01:15:00,000
I'll take him under the stairs
and do him like the others.

692
01:15:00,440 --> 01:15:03,040
- Only it won't be his ears I cut off.
- His balls!

693
01:15:05,400 --> 01:15:07,320
Here, hold this.

694
01:15:15,920 --> 01:15:18,840
Listen, Alice. They're not your real parents.

695
01:15:19,280 --> 01:15:21,240
They're not even husband and wife.

696
01:15:21,960 --> 01:15:25,160
They stole you, like they did
Roach and all the others.

697
01:15:25,800 --> 01:15:28,080
They're a bunch of
rotten baby snatchers.

698
01:15:28,280 --> 01:15:31,520
- You're just saying that.
- My grandfather Booker told me.

699
01:15:32,280 --> 01:15:34,360
He wouldn't lie to me.

700
01:15:37,480 --> 01:15:39,440
What do we do now?

701
01:15:40,600 --> 01:15:42,480
Feel up to a little jump?

702
01:15:42,720 --> 01:15:45,560
The problem is, first thing he did
when you escaped was drain it...

703
01:15:46,160 --> 01:15:48,560
..and put broken glass and rocks
in the bottom.

704
01:15:49,000 --> 01:15:50,240
That's a problem.

705
01:15:50,600 --> 01:15:53,200
The way we came up before
he's got fixed now.

706
01:15:59,920 --> 01:16:01,440
Look.

707
01:16:01,920 --> 01:16:05,680
- This place is one big bomb.
- He's got 'em all over the house.

708
01:16:07,120 --> 01:16:10,080
- Think you could climb the roof?
- What's up there?

709
01:16:13,320 --> 01:16:14,680
The only way out.

710
01:16:22,160 --> 01:16:25,480
- How dare he come into our home?
- He came back to get Alice!

711
01:16:26,040 --> 01:16:29,440
- You should have let me kill her.
- You stay away from Alice!

712
01:16:30,200 --> 01:16:32,800
- She did it with him, I know it.
- Not my little girl!

713
01:16:33,280 --> 01:16:35,200
She's a whore!

714
01:16:46,200 --> 01:16:48,120
What is that?

715
01:17:00,400 --> 01:17:02,120
Oh, God!

716
01:17:02,560 --> 01:17:05,160
- That hurts so bad!

717
01:17:09,520 --> 01:17:11,440
See him?

718
01:17:12,480 --> 01:17:14,480
I can't see shit!

719
01:17:15,840 --> 01:17:17,440
Let me see the brick.

720
01:17:18,000 --> 01:17:19,880
Hold it. I think I hear somethin'.

721
01:17:20,720 --> 01:17:21,640
Bombs away.

722
01:17:22,160 --> 01:17:23,360
- No!

723
01:17:24,000 --> 01:17:25,960
- Argh!

724
01:17:27,120 --> 01:17:29,000
I guess it was one of those smart bricks.

725
01:17:29,600 --> 01:17:31,240
You bastard!

726
01:17:31,600 --> 01:17:34,600
Come on. You can do it.
Just brace yourself on the side.

727
01:17:41,560 --> 01:17:43,040
This is it. Hang on.

728
01:17:50,320 --> 01:17:51,800
The gun!

729
01:18:09,680 --> 01:18:11,160
Ca-ca!

730
01:18:14,240 --> 01:18:16,640
- Hold it. Do you know where we are?
- Uh-uh.

731
01:18:17,720 --> 01:18:19,960
There's the living room.
Get out the back door.

732
01:18:20,280 --> 01:18:23,400
- Fool, come with me.
- I'm not finished with them yet.

733
01:18:26,400 --> 01:18:28,240
- Fool...
- Go!

734
01:18:29,080 --> 01:18:31,520
I'm gonna get the shotgun,
set those kids free.

735
01:18:53,360 --> 01:18:55,440
I... I will get them.

736
01:19:15,400 --> 01:19:17,000
Sh!

737
01:19:22,120 --> 01:19:24,080
Hold it right there!

738
01:19:25,000 --> 01:19:27,520
Where is that little bastard? Tell me!

739
01:19:28,360 --> 01:19:30,840
- Tell me!
- I... I won't tell you.

740
01:19:31,640 --> 01:19:33,760
We will get him out of our house!

741
01:19:35,000 --> 01:19:38,560
He's filthy! He's bad. He's awful!

742
01:19:44,080 --> 01:19:45,760
Go to hell!

743
01:19:50,880 --> 01:19:52,000
Eldon!

744
01:19:53,040 --> 01:19:56,680
Oh, God! He's turned
my little girl against me!

745
01:19:59,040 --> 01:20:01,040
I told you. Those two...

746
01:20:02,320 --> 01:20:04,360
Then she can burn in hell.

747
01:20:05,800 --> 01:20:07,760
Both of them.

748
01:20:16,120 --> 01:20:18,720
She doesn't have a key. She's still in here!

749
01:20:40,960 --> 01:20:42,920
- She's in the cellar.
- No way.

750
01:20:43,840 --> 01:20:45,800
Then he is.

751
01:20:50,000 --> 01:20:51,760
You know a prayer?

752
01:20:52,000 --> 01:20:53,680
You say it.

753
01:21:04,800 --> 01:21:06,880
Shoot her if you see her.

754
01:21:15,960 --> 01:21:17,960
Come here!

755
01:21:26,120 --> 01:21:27,960
See your friends?

756
01:21:31,760 --> 01:21:33,760
- Get him?
- Oh, yeah.

757
01:21:39,920 --> 01:21:42,560
Sh! It may be the police again. Hold on.

758
01:22:03,800 --> 01:22:07,200
My name is Ruby. I represent the
Association of People Unjustly Evicted,...

759
01:22:07,920 --> 01:22:10,320
-.. Exploited and Generally Fucked Over.
- What?

760
01:22:10,600 --> 01:22:13,200
You and your brother are
landlords of over 5O buildings...

761
01:22:13,840 --> 01:22:16,280
..which you allow
to deteriorate into hellholes...

762
01:22:16,720 --> 01:22:19,120
..while you guys get rich
charging ridiculous rents!

763
01:22:19,440 --> 01:22:24,160
Then you evict anyone when they can't
pay so you can tear down their homes.

764
01:22:25,120 --> 01:22:27,760
- Ain't that about right?
- None of your goddamn business!

765
01:22:32,000 --> 01:22:34,040
Kill the little bugger!

766
01:22:35,040 --> 01:22:37,200
Kiss your ass goodbye, boy.

767
01:22:47,320 --> 01:22:50,520
- What the hell is going on?!
- He's loose again! Damn it!

768
01:22:51,800 --> 01:22:54,720
- Police! Open up!

769
01:22:55,640 --> 01:22:56,640
Sh!

770
01:22:59,880 --> 01:23:02,160
Police! We have reports of gunfire!

771
01:23:03,240 --> 01:23:06,320
If you do not open this door,
we'll break it down!

772
01:23:11,720 --> 01:23:14,800
- Get off my property!
- Just want to finish sayin' our piece.

773
01:23:15,360 --> 01:23:18,360
Not only are you bad landlords
but, ten times worse,...

774
01:23:18,920 --> 01:23:22,840
..you've stolen children from
our community for your own sick needs.

775
01:23:23,560 --> 01:23:25,680
There's no community here.

776
01:23:26,920 --> 01:23:28,800
All I see are a couple of n...

777
01:23:28,840 --> 01:23:30,840
Ruby! We're right here.

778
01:23:34,160 --> 01:23:36,240
We busted your ass, bitch!

779
01:23:38,040 --> 01:23:40,160
What are you gonna do? Shoot us all?

780
01:23:40,960 --> 01:23:42,960
- You'll do!
- No!

781
01:23:46,960 --> 01:23:49,160
Damn! You knocked that bitch cold!

782
01:23:49,640 --> 01:23:52,560
Look at her!
What they doin' to her in there?

783
01:24:22,800 --> 01:24:23,680
Oh, shit.

784
01:24:41,200 --> 01:24:43,280
I know you're in here.

785
01:24:44,000 --> 01:24:46,400
You're not gettin' out.

786
01:24:46,880 --> 01:24:49,280
Nobody gets out.

787
01:24:49,640 --> 01:24:51,120
Nobody.

788
01:24:51,920 --> 01:24:53,800
Fool!

789
01:24:57,000 --> 01:24:59,160
Fool? That you?

790
01:25:08,760 --> 01:25:12,080
Listen. There's a way out for you guys,
if you can get past the man.

791
01:25:14,960 --> 01:25:17,760
The door to the outside cellar
got left open.

792
01:25:17,800 --> 01:25:21,640
There you can get outside.
To the sun, to the birds.

793
01:25:23,360 --> 01:25:25,320
To the women.

794
01:25:28,080 --> 01:25:30,120
You wanna give me something?

795
01:25:41,640 --> 01:25:44,680
A burglar alarm? No problem.
I've studied with the best.

796
01:25:48,640 --> 01:25:50,600
I can use these wires to bridge it.

797
01:26:18,360 --> 01:26:20,680
No wonder there's no money in the ghetto.

798
01:26:30,120 --> 01:26:31,840
Fool?

799
01:26:34,400 --> 01:26:36,560
Fool! Fool!

800
01:26:39,000 --> 01:26:41,200
Uh-oh. Your mama's gone.

801
01:26:42,000 --> 01:26:45,040
Oh, shit. Where did that crazy heifer go?

802
01:26:51,920 --> 01:26:55,200
You guys see where she went?
Don't let her get away, you hear?

803
01:26:55,760 --> 01:26:57,440
Wait a minute! Let us help you!

804
01:26:58,920 --> 01:27:00,800
Please! Open the door!

805
01:27:01,760 --> 01:27:03,920
We wanna help you!

806
01:27:10,600 --> 01:27:13,520
System remote override.
All doors locked.

807
01:27:15,800 --> 01:27:18,920
You know I wouldn't
let you get away that easy.

808
01:27:43,000 --> 01:27:45,080
I see you.

809
01:27:48,360 --> 01:27:50,440
And I see you, dearie.

810
01:28:32,400 --> 01:28:34,560
You get back in there! Get back in there!

811
01:28:38,520 --> 01:28:40,400
Don't you touch me!

812
01:28:40,720 --> 01:28:42,440
Don't you touch me! No!

813
01:29:34,720 --> 01:29:36,960
You hurt your mother.

814
01:29:37,400 --> 01:29:39,520
You're not my mother.

815
01:29:40,920 --> 01:29:42,960
You never were.

816
01:29:54,240 --> 01:29:56,400
Then burn in hell!

817
01:30:10,400 --> 01:30:12,280
Mommy!

818
01:31:21,720 --> 01:31:25,360
I know what you're doin'.
You're countin' that money.

819
01:31:25,880 --> 01:31:32,160
You're lettin' it roll through your fingers.
I've done it myself... a thousand times.

820
01:31:33,280 --> 01:31:35,560
And I'll do it again.

821
01:31:36,080 --> 01:31:38,200
But you won't!

822
01:31:55,640 --> 01:31:56,400
Hey!

823
01:31:59,600 --> 01:32:01,760
You shoot me and you die too, man.

824
01:32:02,280 --> 01:32:04,600
And you better believe it.

825
01:32:05,200 --> 01:32:09,160
Don't be crazy, now. There's enough
dynamite there to blow you sky-high.

826
01:32:10,320 --> 01:32:12,680
Not the best place
to store it, in my opinion.

827
01:32:13,240 --> 01:32:15,560
But there it was. Just put the gun down.

828
01:32:17,400 --> 01:32:19,480
Put the gun down.

829
01:32:22,240 --> 01:32:25,960
I don't wanna kill you, but I will,
cos I don't like you much anyway.

830
01:32:30,320 --> 01:32:34,040
I'm tired of fuckin' around,
so either put the gun down now,...

831
01:32:34,640 --> 01:32:37,840
..or kiss your ass goodbye, boy.

832
01:32:45,160 --> 01:32:46,360
Oh, shit!

833
01:33:15,560 --> 01:33:17,040
All right!

834
01:33:22,160 --> 01:33:23,920
Fool?

835
01:33:28,320 --> 01:33:30,280
Fool, are you OK?

836
01:33:35,520 --> 01:33:37,680
I feel like a million dollars.

837
01:33:38,200 --> 01:33:40,960
